  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Validation results are reported from bench-top and in-vitro testing campaigns; however the structured provenance linking those results to their generating activities is absent for the primary hemolysis validation result, constituting the targeted W-EP-02 epistemic gap. Decision: Accepted.",
