      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is version-controlled and regression-tested at the vendor level; however, the site-specific SQA plan covering hemolysis UDFs is incomplete and no independent code review has been performed. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
