    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment package is accepted as a complete submission for review purposes. Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed; all assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing documented epistemic gaps. The primary hemolysis validation result (hemolysis-primary-invitro) is reported without a structured provenance link to its generating activity; the narrative references an in-vitro testing campaign conducted in 2023 but the corresponding Activity IRI is absent from the structured record. This gap is acknowledged and the package is forwarded for regulatory review with the understanding that provenance documentation must be remediated prior to final submission.",
